Text.SourceString: Oh, you’re <PlayerName>$player</>. I’ve heard about you from my uncle, <NPCName>Joko</>… The carpenter.//<portrait=annoyed>Tall? Mustache? No?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, you’re <PlayerName>$player</>. I’ve heard about you from my uncle, <NPCName>Joko</>… The carpenter.//<portrait=annoyed>Tall? Mustache? No?

Text.SourceString: Actually, I also just moved here last Winter, for work.
Text.LocalizedString: Actually, I also just moved here last Winter, for work.

Text.SourceString: I see a lot of potential on this island, and I’m sure I’m not the only one.//I feel like we could build the town up.
Text.LocalizedString: I see a lot of potential on this island, and I’m sure I’m not the only one.//I feel like we could build the town up.

Text.SourceString: Stick with me on this! Picture, if you will, a thriving community garden, a gathering spot.//<portrait=normal>Imagine tending to your plants on a sunny Spring day.
Text.LocalizedString: Stick with me on this! Picture, if you will, a thriving community garden, a gathering spot.//<portrait=normal>Imagine tending to your plants on a sunny Spring day.

Text.SourceString: Reuse your cups when you can, will you?//It can start with us, then hopefully, others will pick it up.
Text.LocalizedString: Reuse your cups when you can, will you?//It can start with us, then hopefully, others will pick it up.

Text.SourceString: Besides, what have you got to lose, am I right?
Text.LocalizedString: Besides, what have you got to lose, am I right?

Text.SourceString: A lot to explore here, huh?
Text.LocalizedString: A lot to explore here, huh?

Text.SourceString: I spent my first month just wandering around the island, getting to know the lay of the land.//<portrait=concerned>Got lost a few times and ended up in the forest...a strange experience.
Text.LocalizedString: I spent my first month just wandering around the island, getting to know the lay of the land.//<portrait=concerned>Got lost a few times and ended up in the forest...a strange experience.

Text.SourceString: I have to admit that before coming here, I had quite a narrow mindset.//<portrait=annoyed>If science didn't back it, I didn't buy into it.
Text.LocalizedString: I have to admit that before coming here, I had quite a narrow mindset.//<portrait=annoyed>If science didn't back it, I didn't buy into it.

Text.SourceString: I’m still like that now to a certain degree.//<portrait=happy>But some things, like fairies… They’re not too far out there, are they?
Text.LocalizedString: I’m still like that now to a certain degree.//<portrait=happy>But some things, like fairies… They’re not too far out there, are they?

Text.SourceString: How are you doing here so far, <PlayerName>$player</>?//<portrait=happy>Does it feel like home yet?
Text.LocalizedString: How are you doing here so far, <PlayerName>$player</>?//<portrait=happy>Does it feel like home yet?

Text.SourceString: Coral Island's become my second home. After studying the local ecosystem, it feels like I'm where I'm supposed to be.
Text.LocalizedString: Coral Island's become my second home. After studying the local ecosystem, it feels like I'm where I'm supposed to be.

Text.SourceString: You live on the large farm by the forest? No way!//<portrait=happy>Beautiful spot. I live next to the forest too.//<portrait=normal>At my Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> and Aunt <NPCName>Dinda’s</> house.
Text.LocalizedString: You live on the large farm by the forest? No way!//<portrait=happy>Beautiful spot. I live next to the forest too.//<portrait=normal>At my Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> and Aunt <NPCName>Dinda’s</> house.

Text.SourceString: Feel free to drop by anytime! Although, fair warning, I'm often out and about.
Text.LocalizedString: Feel free to drop by anytime! Although, fair warning, I'm often out and about.

Text.SourceString: It took me a good year to really familiarize myself with the island and its residents.
Text.LocalizedString: It took me a good year to really familiarize myself with the island and its residents.

Text.SourceString: Looking back, I probably should have gone out more.//<portrait=normal>That would’ve made the process faster.
Text.LocalizedString: Looking back, I probably should have gone out more.//<portrait=normal>That would’ve made the process faster.

Text.SourceString: Be careful in the forest. I was out there when I got caught in a storm.//<portrait=normal>And listen to this. While I was looking for shelter, I found a little cave, so I went in, right?//<portrait=surprised>I mean, anyone would have at that point.
Text.LocalizedString: Be careful in the forest. I was out there when I got caught in a storm.//<portrait=normal>And listen to this. While I was looking for shelter, I found a little cave, so I went in, right?//<portrait=surprised>I mean, anyone would have at that point.

Text.SourceString: Then I realized the cave was actually an old mine.//<portrait=concerned>I dug up a couple of diamonds while I was there.//<portrait=normal>Do you know about this?
Text.LocalizedString: Then I realized the cave was actually an old mine.//<portrait=concerned>I dug up a couple of diamonds while I was there.//<portrait=normal>Do you know about this?

Text.SourceString: The mine is in the very back of the forest, right across the river.
Text.LocalizedString: The mine is in the very back of the forest, right across the river.

Text.SourceString: Umm… Yeah?
Text.LocalizedString: Umm… Yeah?

Text.SourceString: Is everything running smoothly at the farm?
Text.LocalizedString: Is everything running smoothly at the farm?

Text.SourceString: Oh… Errr… Great talk.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh… Errr… Great talk.

Text.SourceString: I’m embarrassed to admit I got lost the other day, trying to find my way back from the forest.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m embarrassed to admit I got lost the other day, trying to find my way back from the forest.

Text.SourceString: I needed to collect some specimens for work, but I lost track of time.//It got dark so quickly. I had no idea.
Text.LocalizedString: I needed to collect some specimens for work, but I lost track of time.//It got dark so quickly. I had no idea.

Text.SourceString: We’re working toward the same goal, to make Coral Island home.//<portrait=happy>Yeah, you and me. We both want the same thing.
Text.LocalizedString: We’re working toward the same goal, to make Coral Island home.//<portrait=happy>Yeah, you and me. We both want the same thing.

Text.SourceString: I’m kinda feeling it now.//<portrait=normal>Coral Island is starting to feel like home.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m kinda feeling it now.//<portrait=normal>Coral Island is starting to feel like home.

Text.SourceString: I like to spend my Saturdays here.//<portrait=happy>You do too, huh?
Text.LocalizedString: I like to spend my Saturdays here.//<portrait=happy>You do too, huh?

Text.SourceString: Maybe I should be more adventurous. I don’t know.//<portrait=normal>I don’t want to rush it.//There’s still plenty of time to explore in the future, right?
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe I should be more adventurous. I don’t know.//<portrait=normal>I don’t want to rush it.//There’s still plenty of time to explore in the future, right?

Text.SourceString: The fellowship with <NPCName>Ling</> doesn’t feel like work at all.//<portrait=happy>I’m glad she accepted my application.
Text.LocalizedString: The fellowship with <NPCName>Ling</> doesn’t feel like work at all.//<portrait=happy>I’m glad she accepted my application.

Text.SourceString: My whole life, I’ve always liked the ocean. I want to spend my time here taking care of it.
Text.LocalizedString: My whole life, I’ve always liked the ocean. I want to spend my time here taking care of it.

Text.SourceString: Kinda miss the lab.//<portrait=annoyed>Work is all I can think of on my day off… *sighs*
Text.LocalizedString: Kinda miss the lab.//<portrait=annoyed>Work is all I can think of on my day off… *sighs*

Text.SourceString: Why am I here chilling when I could be in the lab finishing up reports?
Text.LocalizedString: Why am I here chilling when I could be in the lab finishing up reports?

Text.SourceString: My family runs a boating company over on Puny Island.//My dad still seizes any chance he gets to sail.
Text.LocalizedString: My family runs a boating company over on Puny Island.//My dad still seizes any chance he gets to sail.

Text.SourceString: I've practically been on boats since I was in diapers.
Text.LocalizedString: I've practically been on boats since I was in diapers.

Text.SourceString: I used to spend my Summers on Coral Island, not always this side, though.//<portrait=happy>Most of my Summer breaks were by the sea, diving and swimming with the fish.
Text.LocalizedString: I used to spend my Summers on Coral Island, not always this side, though.//<portrait=happy>Most of my Summer breaks were by the sea, diving and swimming with the fish.

Text.SourceString: I feel connected to them, you know? The coral reefs, the fish.//They're like childhood friends. I grew up alongside these aquatic creatures.
Text.LocalizedString: I feel connected to them, you know? The coral reefs, the fish.//They're like childhood friends. I grew up alongside these aquatic creatures.

Text.SourceString: I can't stand the thought of losing them.//I want my future kids to experience what I had, to see the wonders I saw.
Text.LocalizedString: I can't stand the thought of losing them.//I want my future kids to experience what I had, to see the wonders I saw.

Text.SourceString: Once I finish my fellowship with <NPCName>Ling</>, I'm hoping for a full-time position here.//<portrait=happy>Fingers crossed!
Text.LocalizedString: Once I finish my fellowship with <NPCName>Ling</>, I'm hoping for a full-time position here.//<portrait=happy>Fingers crossed!

Text.SourceString: It’s not easy to find a job in this economy, but it’s not just about a job, you see.//<portrait=normal>It’s about this particular job.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s not easy to find a job in this economy, but it’s not just about a job, you see.//<portrait=normal>It’s about this particular job.

Text.SourceString: Coral Island has one of the most beautiful coral reefs, and I want to study it!//<portrait=normal>I’d love to spend my life doing what I can to protect it from rising sea temperatures.
Text.LocalizedString: Coral Island has one of the most beautiful coral reefs, and I want to study it!//<portrait=normal>I’d love to spend my life doing what I can to protect it from rising sea temperatures.

Text.SourceString: Mermaids, <PlayerName>$player</>? I can't say I believe in them.
Text.LocalizedString: Mermaids, <PlayerName>$player</>? I can't say I believe in them.

Text.SourceString: I’ve dived my whole life, and I’ve never seen a mermaid.//<portrait=normal>Also, I’ve read a lot about the ocean, and nothing ever mentioned the existence of mermaids.//I could easily be wrong, though. The world is full of unanswered mysteries.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve dived my whole life, and I’ve never seen a mermaid.//<portrait=normal>Also, I’ve read a lot about the ocean, and nothing ever mentioned the existence of mermaids.//I could easily be wrong, though. The world is full of unanswered mysteries.

Text.SourceString: Milk? Eek… None for me. I don’t know.//<portrait=normal>I guess it leaves a weird aftertaste.//<portrait=happy>Now, lodeh. That’s where the flavor is at.
Text.LocalizedString: Milk? Eek… None for me. I don’t know.//<portrait=normal>I guess it leaves a weird aftertaste.//<portrait=happy>Now, lodeh. That’s where the flavor is at.

Text.SourceString: You can cook lodeh? I'm impressed!//<portrait=happy>I can’t make lodeh. It’s a bit too complicated for my cooking skills.
Text.LocalizedString: You can cook lodeh? I'm impressed!//<portrait=happy>I can’t make lodeh. It’s a bit too complicated for my cooking skills.

Text.SourceString: Merfolk?! Around Coral Island?
Text.LocalizedString: Merfolk?! Around Coral Island?

Text.SourceString: Interesting, indeed.
Text.LocalizedString: Interesting, indeed.

Text.SourceString: Oh, hey! Happy Saturday!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, hey! Happy Saturday!

Text.SourceString: Drinking too much milk gives me a stomachache. And it has that weird aftertaste.
Text.LocalizedString: Drinking too much milk gives me a stomachache. And it has that weird aftertaste.

Text.SourceString: I never made the connection until I had a minor accident at a theme park…
Text.LocalizedString: I never made the connection until I had a minor accident at a theme park…

Text.SourceString: Minor, <PlayerName>$player</>. It really was nothing. I’ve shared too much. Bye-bye, now.
Text.LocalizedString: Minor, <PlayerName>$player</>. It really was nothing. I’ve shared too much. Bye-bye, now.

Text.SourceString: Tomorrow is work as usual for me. Nope, nothing special planned that I remember.
Text.LocalizedString: Tomorrow is work as usual for me. Nope, nothing special planned that I remember.

Text.SourceString: Oh, umm… I won’t be going out tonight. I have to be at 100 percent tomorrow.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, umm… I won’t be going out tonight. I have to be at 100 percent tomorrow.

Text.SourceString: I didn’t want to be rude by calling <NPCName>Dr. Jiang</>, <NPCName>Ling</>. But she asked me to. It felt really weird at first.
Text.LocalizedString: I didn’t want to be rude by calling <NPCName>Dr. Jiang</>, <NPCName>Ling</>. But she asked me to. It felt really weird at first.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Ling</> said it sounded too formal for her, but she was more than happy to address me as Dr. Widjojo if I preferred.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Ling</> said it sounded too formal for her, but she was more than happy to address me as Dr. Widjojo if I preferred.

Text.SourceString: I declined her offer and said we could keep the environment in the lab casual.
Text.LocalizedString: I declined her offer and said we could keep the environment in the lab casual.

Text.SourceString: How do you think they came up with the name Coral Island?
Text.LocalizedString: How do you think they came up with the name Coral Island?

Text.SourceString: Ouch. Appreciate your honesty, I guess.
Text.LocalizedString: Ouch. Appreciate your honesty, I guess.

Special.SourceString: I think it’s a lazy name. You see coral, you say “coral.”
Special.LocalizedString: I think it’s a lazy name. You see coral, you say “coral.”

57.SpecialTag: I think it’s a lazy name. You see coral, you say “coral.”
57.Question: R1

Text.SourceString: I thought so too. So insightful!
Text.LocalizedString: I thought so too. So insightful!

Special.SourceString: It’s known for coral reefs, so the name is to preserve the legacy, I think.
Special.LocalizedString: It’s known for coral reefs, so the name is to preserve the legacy, I think.

58.SpecialTag: It’s known for coral reefs, so the name is to preserve the legacy, I think.
58.Question: R2

Text.SourceString: Hmm. Very meta. I never thought about it that way. I like it!//You have a great way of looking at things. I like that about you.
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm. Very meta. I never thought about it that way. I like it!//You have a great way of looking at things. I like that about you.

Special.SourceString: A group of faceless people comes to mind. They’re sitting around a circular table, debating it.
Special.LocalizedString: A group of faceless people comes to mind. They’re sitting around a circular table, debating it.

59.SpecialTag: A group of faceless people comes to mind. They’re sitting around a circular table, debating it.
59.Question: R3

Text.SourceString: Tomorrow is work as usual for me. Nope, nothing special planned that I remember.
Text.LocalizedString: Tomorrow is work as usual for me. Nope, nothing special planned that I remember.

Text.SourceString: Oh, umm… I won’t be going out tonight. I have to be at 100 percent tomorrow.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, umm… I won’t be going out tonight. I have to be at 100 percent tomorrow.

Text.SourceString: I'm catching up with some friends at Fishensips this Friday.//Nothing grand, just a casual meet-up, maybe some pool.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm catching up with some friends at Fishensips this Friday.//Nothing grand, just a casual meet-up, maybe some pool.

Text.SourceString: It's laid-back, you should join!
Text.LocalizedString: It's laid-back, you should join!

Text.SourceString: There isn't a single store on this island that operates seven days a week.
Text.LocalizedString: There isn't a single store on this island that operates seven days a week.

Text.SourceString: It’s a good thing in the era of twenty-four-seven convenience, I say.//It teaches us patience.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s a good thing in the era of twenty-four-seven convenience, I say.//It teaches us patience.

Text.SourceString: Except for the clinic. They always have someone on call in case of emergency.
Text.LocalizedString: Except for the clinic. They always have someone on call in case of emergency.

Text.SourceString: Silence doesn’t bother me. I’m used to being in a lab all day and night. In fact, I really can’t work well in a room full of people.
Text.LocalizedString: Silence doesn’t bother me. I’m used to being in a lab all day and night. In fact, I really can’t work well in a room full of people.

Text.SourceString: I make it a point not to bring my work home. It's too chaotic.//Besides, <NPCName>Archie</> can be pretty noisy. It’s just too hard for me to focus.
Text.LocalizedString: I make it a point not to bring my work home. It's too chaotic.//Besides, <NPCName>Archie</> can be pretty noisy. It’s just too hard for me to focus.

Text.SourceString: Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> makes sure I don’t skip any festivals, because he doesn’t want me to miss all the fun.
Text.LocalizedString: Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> makes sure I don’t skip any festivals, because he doesn’t want me to miss all the fun.

Text.SourceString: I oblige.
Text.LocalizedString: I oblige.

Text.SourceString: Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> is Dad’s brother. You’ve never met Dad, but they kind of look alike. I think I look like Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> a bit, no?
Text.LocalizedString: Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> is Dad’s brother. You’ve never met Dad, but they kind of look alike. I think I look like Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> a bit, no?

Text.SourceString: It’s my eyes, I think. We all have the same eyes. It’s in our genes.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s my eyes, I think. We all have the same eyes. It’s in our genes.

Text.SourceString: The water’s starting to warm up.//<portrait=sad>But it’s still too cold for me.
Text.LocalizedString: The water’s starting to warm up.//<portrait=sad>But it’s still too cold for me.

Text.SourceString: I was helping Aunt <NPCName>Dinda</> weed the crops.//Spring is <Italic>finally</> here, isn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: I was helping Aunt <NPCName>Dinda</> weed the crops.//Spring is <Italic>finally</> here, isn’t it?

Text.SourceString: Sakura trees normally only blossom for a two-week period… Two or three weeks, something like that.//It isn’t usually a whole-season thing, but it is here. Must be something special in the water.
Text.LocalizedString: Sakura trees normally only blossom for a two-week period… Two or three weeks, something like that.//It isn’t usually a whole-season thing, but it is here. Must be something special in the water.

Text.SourceString: The lake is stunning during Spring, with pink petals everywhere. I'm more of an ocean guy though.//<portrait=normal>I find something oddly comforting about the saltwater. Is that weird? Ha ha.
Text.LocalizedString: The lake is stunning during Spring, with pink petals everywhere. I'm more of an ocean guy though.//<portrait=normal>I find something oddly comforting about the saltwater. Is that weird? Ha ha.

Text.SourceString: I’m so glad Winter’s over with.//<portrait=happy>I feel a lot better now…
Text.LocalizedString: I’m so glad Winter’s over with.//<portrait=happy>I feel a lot better now…

Text.SourceString: The hot spring near our house is sometimes visited by wildlife, like monkeys.//Especially in the colder seasons, like now. But I read somewhere they go there to relax rather than keep warm.//Their thick coats keep them plenty warm.
Text.LocalizedString: The hot spring near our house is sometimes visited by wildlife, like monkeys.//Especially in the colder seasons, like now. But I read somewhere they go there to relax rather than keep warm.//Their thick coats keep them plenty warm.

Text.SourceString: We should be able to see seals chilling at the beach this time of year.//Some are shedding their old coats, and some are there to get away from predators.//That’s what I read online, anyway.
Text.LocalizedString: We should be able to see seals chilling at the beach this time of year.//Some are shedding their old coats, and some are there to get away from predators.//That’s what I read online, anyway.

Text.SourceString: There’s nothing like going to the ocean on a hot Summer day.//Except for eating melon…
Text.LocalizedString: There’s nothing like going to the ocean on a hot Summer day.//Except for eating melon…

Text.SourceString: This is my kind of weather, <PlayerName>$player</>. Hot, humid, sun blazing down. Love it.
Text.LocalizedString: This is my kind of weather, <PlayerName>$player</>. Hot, humid, sun blazing down. Love it.

Text.SourceString: If you get too exhausted at the beach...sun does that to you...go to the Beach Shack to cool off and get some coconut water.
Text.LocalizedString: If you get too exhausted at the beach...sun does that to you...go to the Beach Shack to cool off and get some coconut water.

Text.SourceString: The beach in Summer brings back some childhood memories.//Eating corn on the cob at sunset was the best Summer treat, back in the day.
Text.LocalizedString: The beach in Summer brings back some childhood memories.//Eating corn on the cob at sunset was the best Summer treat, back in the day.

Text.SourceString: The water here stays warm in the evening…//It isn’t too cold to dive at night. In the Summer, though… I don’t know about any other season.
Text.LocalizedString: The water here stays warm in the evening…//It isn’t too cold to dive at night. In the Summer, though… I don’t know about any other season.

Text.SourceString: Different seasons bring different varieties of coconuts here.//<portrait=concerned>If I'm not mistaken, Summer is when we get the...macapuno coconut, or was it the coral tall?
Text.LocalizedString: Different seasons bring different varieties of coconuts here.//<portrait=concerned>If I'm not mistaken, Summer is when we get the...macapuno coconut, or was it the coral tall?

Text.SourceString: The only time I truly feel at home here is when Summer hits and the heat rises. I guess I’m just a tropical boy at heart!
Text.LocalizedString: The only time I truly feel at home here is when Summer hits and the heat rises. I guess I’m just a tropical boy at heart!

Text.SourceString: It’s starting to get chilly. I hope it doesn’t get any colder than this.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s starting to get chilly. I hope it doesn’t get any colder than this.

Text.SourceString: One thing I like about Fall is the fresh mushrooms. You can make polenta with them, and nothing beats freshly harvested mushrooms!
Text.LocalizedString: One thing I like about Fall is the fresh mushrooms. You can make polenta with them, and nothing beats freshly harvested mushrooms!

Text.SourceString: I love the Harvest Festival. It’s a good example of just how close-knit this community is.//<portrait=concerned>But then there are the Beluga Bay farmers…
Text.LocalizedString: I love the Harvest Festival. It’s a good example of just how close-knit this community is.//<portrait=concerned>But then there are the Beluga Bay farmers…

Text.SourceString: It’s mushroom season, all right! Going to the forest to forage anytime soon?//Me? Nope, I don’t think so. I’m scared I might get lost.//<portrait=concerned>Maybe if I can get my uncle to come with me…
Text.LocalizedString: It’s mushroom season, all right! Going to the forest to forage anytime soon?//Me? Nope, I don’t think so. I’m scared I might get lost.//<portrait=concerned>Maybe if I can get my uncle to come with me…

Text.SourceString: Do you know where I can get some bamboo shoots in Fall?//I went looking for them around the hot spring. No luck.
Text.LocalizedString: Do you know where I can get some bamboo shoots in Fall?//I went looking for them around the hot spring. No luck.

Text.SourceString: I didn’t realize Winters here were so cold!
Text.LocalizedString: I didn’t realize Winters here were so cold!

Text.SourceString: I don’t think I’ll ever get used to Winter.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t think I’ll ever get used to Winter.

Text.SourceString: I don’t understand how some people can go out in this weather wearing only two layers.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t understand how some people can go out in this weather wearing only two layers.

Text.SourceString: I tried diving the other day, and it was so cold! It was horrible!//How do you do it?
Text.LocalizedString: I tried diving the other day, and it was so cold! It was horrible!//How do you do it?

Text.SourceString: I try not to go into the water during Winter. It’s too cold.// For now, above-sea-level testing only.
Text.LocalizedString: I try not to go into the water during Winter. It’s too cold.// For now, above-sea-level testing only.

Text.SourceString: It’s too cold, <PlayerName>$player</>. Too cold.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s too cold, <PlayerName>$player</>. Too cold.

Text.SourceString: Are there really two more weeks of Winter? I don’t know if I can last through it.
Text.LocalizedString: Are there really two more weeks of Winter? I don’t know if I can last through it.

Text.SourceString: The New Year’s Eve Festival is going to be right behind our house. So there’s no point in not going.//You wouldn’t be able to sleep or do anything anyway. It’ll be way too loud.
Text.LocalizedString: The New Year’s Eve Festival is going to be right behind our house. So there’s no point in not going.//You wouldn’t be able to sleep or do anything anyway. It’ll be way too loud.

Text.SourceString: This island is famous, huh? I’ve been noticing a lot of new people moving here lately.//<portrait=concerned>There was me, then it was you, and now the Pufferfish Corp.
Text.LocalizedString: This island is famous, huh? I’ve been noticing a lot of new people moving here lately.//<portrait=concerned>There was me, then it was you, and now the Pufferfish Corp.

Text.SourceString: Good point. I did come here for work.//And so did Pufferfish.
Text.LocalizedString: Good point. I did come here for work.//And so did Pufferfish.

Text.SourceString: My parents never asked too much of me.//Just to make sure I remember to share what I have with the community.
Text.LocalizedString: My parents never asked too much of me.//Just to make sure I remember to share what I have with the community.

Text.SourceString: I know it isn’t for everybody, but that’s how I was brought up.//We need to take care of each other.
Text.LocalizedString: I know it isn’t for everybody, but that’s how I was brought up.//We need to take care of each other.

Text.SourceString: Have you met <NPCName>Nina</>?//We met at the beach and got to talking a bit.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you met <NPCName>Nina</>?//We met at the beach and got to talking a bit.

Text.SourceString: Apparently, she lives in the abandoned villa on the beach and now only comes here for Summer.
Text.LocalizedString: Apparently, she lives in the abandoned villa on the beach and now only comes here for Summer.

Text.SourceString: Wow, that felt gossipy. Heh!
Text.LocalizedString: Wow, that felt gossipy. Heh!

Text.SourceString: Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> tells me festivals are a great way to meet everybody, especially since I’m new around here.
Text.LocalizedString: Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> tells me festivals are a great way to meet everybody, especially since I’m new around here.

Text.SourceString: The beach cleanup is on the 28th, right?//<portrait=concerned>Umm… I think.
Text.LocalizedString: The beach cleanup is on the 28th, right?//<portrait=concerned>Umm… I think.

Text.SourceString: Uh… My mistake. I think it’s on the 27th.//<portrait=normal>I got it mixed up with the one back on Puny Island.
Text.LocalizedString: Uh… My mistake. I think it’s on the 27th.//<portrait=normal>I got it mixed up with the one back on Puny Island.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Dr. Ling</> and I recycle all the trash collected during the beach cleanup.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Dr. Ling</> and I recycle all the trash collected during the beach cleanup.

Text.SourceString: We turn it into materials for the town to use to fix community buildings or broken pavement.
Text.LocalizedString: We turn it into materials for the town to use to fix community buildings or broken pavement.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Nina</> is smart and humble. I feel like I could talk to her all day, and I usually have a hard time chatting with people.//<portrait=normal>But with her, it just flows, you know?
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Nina</> is smart and humble. I feel like I could talk to her all day, and I usually have a hard time chatting with people.//<portrait=normal>But with her, it just flows, you know?

Text.SourceString: I’m blabbering again.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m blabbering again.

Text.SourceString: I need to crank up the heater tonight. It looks like it’s gonna be a heck of a night.
Text.LocalizedString: I need to crank up the heater tonight. It looks like it’s gonna be a heck of a night.

Text.SourceString: Don’t freeze at the farm, okay? Heh heh.
Text.LocalizedString: Don’t freeze at the farm, okay? Heh heh.

Text.SourceString: The house smells wonderful lately because Aunt <NPCName>Dinda</> has been busy testing recipes for the cooking competition.
Text.LocalizedString: The house smells wonderful lately because Aunt <NPCName>Dinda</> has been busy testing recipes for the cooking competition.

Text.SourceString: I’ll go with the rest of the family to watch the contest, but I don’t think I’ll enter this year.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ll go with the rest of the family to watch the contest, but I don’t think I’ll enter this year.

Text.SourceString: I can’t believe I’ve already been living here for a whole year.
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t believe I’ve already been living here for a whole year.

Text.SourceString: They’re right. Time does fly when you’re having fun.
Text.LocalizedString: They’re right. Time does fly when you’re having fun.

Text.SourceString: It’s my second year going to the Winter Fair.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s my second year going to the Winter Fair.

Text.SourceString: It was so much fun last year. I definitely won’t miss it this year.
Text.LocalizedString: It was so much fun last year. I definitely won’t miss it this year.

Text.SourceString: For some reason, I concentrate better during Winter. I think it might be the cold.//Or maybe it’s because of the quiet.
Text.LocalizedString: For some reason, I concentrate better during Winter. I think it might be the cold.//Or maybe it’s because of the quiet.

Text.SourceString: That said, I definitely blame the cold for waking me up early. Heh heh.
Text.LocalizedString: That said, I definitely blame the cold for waking me up early. Heh heh.

Text.SourceString: For some reason, people feel the need to talk about the rain when it’s raining.
Text.LocalizedString: For some reason, people feel the need to talk about the rain when it’s raining.

Text.SourceString: Like the phenomenon is so surprising.
Text.LocalizedString: Like the phenomenon is so surprising.

Text.SourceString: Eventually, I want to publish more articles or even a book about my findings.
Text.LocalizedString: Eventually, I want to publish more articles or even a book about my findings.

Text.SourceString: One step at a time, though. Yeah.//<portrait=happy>Don’t get too excited yet!
Text.LocalizedString: One step at a time, though. Yeah.//<portrait=happy>Don’t get too excited yet!

Text.SourceString: I’m soaking wet.//Excuse me, I just wanna be indoors.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m soaking wet.//Excuse me, I just wanna be indoors.

Text.SourceString: I’m soaking wet.//Excuse me, I just wanna be indoors.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m soaking wet.//Excuse me, I just wanna be indoors.

Text.SourceString: I’m soaking wet.//Excuse me, I just wanna be indoors.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m soaking wet.//Excuse me, I just wanna be indoors.

Text.SourceString: I’m soaking wet.//Excuse me, I just wanna be indoors.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m soaking wet.//Excuse me, I just wanna be indoors.

Text.SourceString: For some reason, people feel the need to talk about the storm when it’s storming.
Text.LocalizedString: For some reason, people feel the need to talk about the storm when it’s storming.

Text.SourceString: Like the phenomenon is so surprising.
Text.LocalizedString: Like the phenomenon is so surprising.

Text.SourceString: Eventually, I want to publish more articles or even a book about my findings.
Text.LocalizedString: Eventually, I want to publish more articles or even a book about my findings.

Text.SourceString: One step at a time, though. Yeah.//<portrait=happy>Don’t get too excited yet!
Text.LocalizedString: One step at a time, though. Yeah.//<portrait=happy>Don’t get too excited yet!

Text.SourceString: Oh, you’re still here. It’s a bit late, isn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, you’re still here. It’s a bit late, isn’t it?

Text.SourceString: Why are you still here? Umm…
Text.LocalizedString: Why are you still here? Umm…

Text.SourceString: Oh, you’re still here. It’s a bit late, isn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, you’re still here. It’s a bit late, isn’t it?

Text.SourceString: Why are you still here? Umm…
Text.LocalizedString: Why are you still here? Umm…

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Dr. Jiang</> published a couple of books and a lot of scholarly articles about her research here.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Dr. Jiang</> published a couple of books and a lot of scholarly articles about her research here.

Text.SourceString: I read them all and even used a couple as references for presentations back in school.//<portrait=normal>She finds fascinating subjects to cover.
Text.LocalizedString: I read them all and even used a couple as references for presentations back in school.//<portrait=normal>She finds fascinating subjects to cover.

Text.SourceString: It’s still snowing out, huh?//<portrait=sad>I should’ve worn a thicker jacket.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s still snowing out, huh?//<portrait=sad>I should’ve worn a thicker jacket.

Text.SourceString: I hope you have extra blankets in the cabin, <PlayerName>$player</>.//This snow doesn’t look like it’s going to be slowing down anytime soon.
Text.LocalizedString: I hope you have extra blankets in the cabin, <PlayerName>$player</>.//This snow doesn’t look like it’s going to be slowing down anytime soon.

Text.SourceString: Keep warm, okay?
Text.LocalizedString: Keep warm, okay?

Text.SourceString: I’m very cold.//Excuse me, I just wanna be indoors.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m very cold.//Excuse me, I just wanna be indoors.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Dr. Jiang</> published a couple of books and a lot of scholarly articles about her research here.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Dr. Jiang</> published a couple of books and a lot of scholarly articles about her research here.

Text.SourceString: I read them all and even used a couple as references for presentations back in school.//She covers fascinating subjects.
Text.LocalizedString: I read them all and even used a couple as references for presentations back in school.//She covers fascinating subjects.

Text.SourceString: Did I bum you out?//Maybe I should stop talking about work.
Text.LocalizedString: Did I bum you out?//Maybe I should stop talking about work.

Text.SourceString: In the future, I want to publish more academic articles or even a book about my findings.
Text.LocalizedString: In the future, I want to publish more academic articles or even a book about my findings.

Text.SourceString: I have to remind myself it’s one step at a time.//<portrait=sad>I can’t rush it, or I might fail altogether.
Text.LocalizedString: I have to remind myself it’s one step at a time.//<portrait=sad>I can’t rush it, or I might fail altogether.

Text.SourceString: There’s another scientist I’d like to do a fellowship under.//<portrait=concerned>But I don’t think he’s currently accepting applications.
Text.LocalizedString: There’s another scientist I’d like to do a fellowship under.//<portrait=concerned>But I don’t think he’s currently accepting applications.

Text.SourceString: He lives in Mount Yahara, not far from here. But you need to take a boat and then a bus across the desert to get there.
Text.LocalizedString: He lives in Mount Yahara, not far from here. But you need to take a boat and then a bus across the desert to get there.

Text.SourceString: The wind is so cold today.//I can literally feel it in my bones.
Text.LocalizedString: The wind is so cold today.//I can literally feel it in my bones.

Text.SourceString: Maybe I should go to the clinic and see if that’s normal.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe I should go to the clinic and see if that’s normal.

Text.SourceString: I work for <NPCName>Dr. Ling</> down at the lab. She's the real deal!
Text.LocalizedString: I work for <NPCName>Dr. Ling</> down at the lab. She's the real deal!

Text.SourceString: No, she didn’t make me say that. Just giving credit where it's due.
Text.LocalizedString: No, she didn’t make me say that. Just giving credit where it's due.

Text.SourceString: You should check out Socket & Pan. It's run by <NPCName>Luke</>. Tell him I sent you!
Text.LocalizedString: You should check out Socket & Pan. It's run by <NPCName>Luke</>. Tell him I sent you!

Text.SourceString: Watching Aunt <NPCName>Dinda</> and Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> in their workshop is amazing. They have some serious skills.
Text.LocalizedString: Watching Aunt <NPCName>Dinda</> and Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> in their workshop is amazing. They have some serious skills.

Text.SourceString: Wish I was handy like that.
Text.LocalizedString: Wish I was handy like that.

Text.SourceString: Have you spotted those oil rigs around the island? That's Pufferfish Corporation's doing.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you spotted those oil rigs around the island? That's Pufferfish Corporation's doing.

Text.SourceString: Don’t let their propaganda fool you. If they start drilling, it’ll be a disaster for the nearby coral communities!
Text.LocalizedString: Don’t let their propaganda fool you. If they start drilling, it’ll be a disaster for the nearby coral communities!

Text.SourceString: They need to be stopped before it’s too late.
Text.LocalizedString: They need to be stopped before it’s too late.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Archie</> is Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> and Aunt <NPCName>Dinda’s</> son. I think he wants to be a vet one day.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Archie</> is Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> and Aunt <NPCName>Dinda’s</> son. I think he wants to be a vet one day.

Text.SourceString: Even with my PhD in marine biology, it was tough landing a good job.//I mean, I applied everywhere!
Text.LocalizedString: Even with my PhD in marine biology, it was tough landing a good job.//I mean, I applied everywhere!

Text.SourceString: Can't thank <NPCName>Ling</> enough for giving me this chance on Coral Island.
Text.LocalizedString: Can't thank <NPCName>Ling</> enough for giving me this chance on Coral Island.

Text.SourceString: I love eating fresh vegetables from Aunt <NPCName>Dinda’s</> garden.//She’s also an amazing cook.
Text.LocalizedString: I love eating fresh vegetables from Aunt <NPCName>Dinda’s</> garden.//She’s also an amazing cook.

Text.SourceString: Did you know one out of every four marine species lives in coral reefs? Mind-blowing, right?
Text.LocalizedString: Did you know one out of every four marine species lives in coral reefs? Mind-blowing, right?

Text.SourceString: I like to think I'm pretty chill. Hopefully, people see that.
Text.LocalizedString: I like to think I'm pretty chill. Hopefully, people see that.

Text.SourceString: I love rainy days, but I hate carrying an umbrella. I’d rather just get wet.
Text.LocalizedString: I love rainy days, but I hate carrying an umbrella. I’d rather just get wet.

Text.SourceString: Have you tried the tacos at Fishensips? They’re delicious!//I guess it’s called Fishensips now. Back in the day, when I was a little kid, it was called the Local Tavern.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you tried the tacos at Fishensips? They’re delicious!//I guess it’s called Fishensips now. Back in the day, when I was a little kid, it was called the Local Tavern.

Text.SourceString: I don’t mind living with Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> and Aunt <NPCName>Dinda</>, but I...never mind.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t mind living with Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> and Aunt <NPCName>Dinda</>, but I...never mind.

Text.SourceString: I'm lucky. Working at the lab is so cool, it doesn't even feel like a job.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm lucky. Working at the lab is so cool, it doesn't even feel like a job.

Text.SourceString: We have so many exciting projects going on in the lab! Stop by sometime, and I’ll show you around.
Text.LocalizedString: We have so many exciting projects going on in the lab! Stop by sometime, and I’ll show you around.

Text.SourceString: I saw <NPCName>Archie</> playing with Taco the other day. It was cute!//<portrait=normal>They seem to have their own little language going on.
Text.LocalizedString: I saw <NPCName>Archie</> playing with Taco the other day. It was cute!//<portrait=normal>They seem to have their own little language going on.

Text.SourceString: I’m a scientist.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m a scientist.

Text.SourceString: I know, I know, you've heard it before. But I just love saying it.//Yup, I'm a scientist!
Text.LocalizedString: I know, I know, you've heard it before. But I just love saying it.//Yup, I'm a scientist!

Text.SourceString: It’s freezing outside! I’m glad it’s warm and cozy in my lab. I spend most of my time there anyway.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s freezing outside! I’m glad it’s warm and cozy in my lab. I spend most of my time there anyway.

Text.SourceString: Finally, it's warm enough to hit the beach again!
Text.LocalizedString: Finally, it's warm enough to hit the beach again!

Text.SourceString: It’s howling out there!
Text.LocalizedString: It’s howling out there!

Text.SourceString: What a beautiful day for a swim!
Text.LocalizedString: What a beautiful day for a swim!

Text.SourceString: I still pinch myself that I'm here on Coral Island, being a scientist, studying coral reefs and stuff.
Text.LocalizedString: I still pinch myself that I'm here on Coral Island, being a scientist, studying coral reefs and stuff.

Text.SourceString: Well, I guess I did have those ocean posters all over my room as a kid...so, maybe not so surprising.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, I guess I did have those ocean posters all over my room as a kid...so, maybe not so surprising.

Text.SourceString: My aunt thinks you’re a great farmer. Now, that’s one heck of a compliment, since she’s a great gardener herself.//<portrait=happy>She also said you’re a very kind person. Heart of gold.
Text.LocalizedString: My aunt thinks you’re a great farmer. Now, that’s one heck of a compliment, since she’s a great gardener herself.//<portrait=happy>She also said you’re a very kind person. Heart of gold.

Text.SourceString: She isn’t the only one who thinks so, by the way. I feel the same way about you.
Text.LocalizedString: She isn’t the only one who thinks so, by the way. I feel the same way about you.

Text.SourceString: How do you think they came up with the name Coral Island?
Text.LocalizedString: How do you think they came up with the name Coral Island?

Text.SourceString: Or rather, <Italic>who</> do you think started calling it Coral Island?
Text.LocalizedString: Or rather, <Italic>who</> do you think started calling it Coral Island?

Text.SourceString: Having you moving onto Coral Island a month after I did was exciting.//<portrait=happy>I couldn’t wait to meet you. Made me feel like I had a friend to figure out Coral Island with together. Ha ha!
Text.LocalizedString: Having you moving onto Coral Island a month after I did was exciting.//<portrait=happy>I couldn’t wait to meet you. Made me feel like I had a friend to figure out Coral Island with together. Ha ha!

Text.SourceString: I wrote my thesis on how ethical dilemmas impact coral reefs and fish communities.//Quite a quirky topic, so it took me a bit to wrap it up.
Text.LocalizedString: I wrote my thesis on how ethical dilemmas impact coral reefs and fish communities.//Quite a quirky topic, so it took me a bit to wrap it up.

Text.SourceString: I even managed to get a book out of my research.//Got a few copies lying around in my room.
Text.LocalizedString: I even managed to get a book out of my research.//Got a few copies lying around in my room.

Text.SourceString: I think the library might have my book too. But I'm not sure if it's out on the shelves yet.//<portrait=concerned>< NPCName>Millie</> has her hands full with all those books and donations.
Text.LocalizedString: I think the library might have my book too. But I'm not sure if it's out on the shelves yet.//<portrait=concerned>< NPCName>Millie</> has her hands full with all those books and donations.

Text.SourceString: If you spot my book, give it a read! Would love to get your thoughts on it.
Text.LocalizedString: If you spot my book, give it a read! Would love to get your thoughts on it.

Text.SourceString: Looking sharp, <PlayerName>$player</>. Heading out for a wild weekend?
Text.LocalizedString: Looking sharp, <PlayerName>$player</>. Heading out for a wild weekend?

Text.SourceString: I gotta say, I haven't met anyone quite like you before.//You're smart, courageous. Gosh, the list goes on.
Text.LocalizedString: I gotta say, I haven't met anyone quite like you before.//You're smart, courageous. Gosh, the list goes on.

Text.SourceString: Would it be too cheesy if I said I sometimes stroll by your farm just to catch a glimpse of you?
Text.LocalizedString: Would it be too cheesy if I said I sometimes stroll by your farm just to catch a glimpse of you?

Text.SourceString: I don’t know. I just really…wanted to see you.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t know. I just really…wanted to see you.

Text.SourceString: I plan on writing more books once I gather enough data. Maybe something about Coral Island.//<portrait=sad>But sometimes I feel like I'll never be done studying, you know? Everything on this island is interconnected – the ocean, the soil…
Text.LocalizedString: I plan on writing more books once I gather enough data. Maybe something about Coral Island.//<portrait=sad>But sometimes I feel like I'll never be done studying, you know? Everything on this island is interconnected – the ocean, the soil…

Text.SourceString: There’s so much to look into and research.//<portrait=normal>I hope we can use what we learn here and apply it all over the world. The importance of recycling, for instance.
Text.LocalizedString: There’s so much to look into and research.//<portrait=normal>I hope we can use what we learn here and apply it all over the world. The importance of recycling, for instance.

Text.SourceString: You don't think all scientists are nerds, do you?
Text.LocalizedString: You don't think all scientists are nerds, do you?

Text.SourceString: Unless you're into nerds, then it's all good.
Text.LocalizedString: Unless you're into nerds, then it's all good.

Text.SourceString: I know not dating anyone can look lonely at times, but to be honest, I’m not.//Even when I’m alone a lot, you see. At the lab, working late into the night. Or in the field. Sometimes, I go months without socializing.//<portrait=happy>But to tell you the truth, I feel perfectly fine.
Text.LocalizedString: I know not dating anyone can look lonely at times, but to be honest, I’m not.//Even when I’m alone a lot, you see. At the lab, working late into the night. Or in the field. Sometimes, I go months without socializing.//<portrait=happy>But to tell you the truth, I feel perfectly fine.

Text.SourceString: I’m okay if I end up going through life without ever finding a companion.//I feel like I already have a pretty great family.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m okay if I end up going through life without ever finding a companion.//I feel like I already have a pretty great family.

Text.SourceString: For me, it doesn’t really matter where we are. As long as I’m with you, I think we’ll have a good time.
Text.LocalizedString: For me, it doesn’t really matter where we are. As long as I’m with you, I think we’ll have a good time.

Text.SourceString: I could just sit and listen to you all day. You’re intelligent, and the way you think about stuff is…um…very insightful.//<portrait=happy>I learn something new every time I see you.
Text.LocalizedString: I could just sit and listen to you all day. You’re intelligent, and the way you think about stuff is…um…very insightful.//<portrait=happy>I learn something new every time I see you.

Text.SourceString: My job is important to me, but not as important as family.//<portrait=normal>Family is always my first priority. It might sound extreme, but if my parents needed me, I'd be on the first boat home.
Text.LocalizedString: My job is important to me, but not as important as family.//<portrait=normal>Family is always my first priority. It might sound extreme, but if my parents needed me, I'd be on the first boat home.

Text.SourceString: Thing is, they know how much I love my job, so if they did ask me to leave, it'd be for something really important.
Text.LocalizedString: Thing is, they know how much I love my job, so if they did ask me to leave, it'd be for something really important.

Text.SourceString: We’ve never met each other’s parents, huh, <PlayerName>$player</>?//<portrait=normal>Well… You know my uncle pretty well, though, so that counts.
Text.LocalizedString: We’ve never met each other’s parents, huh, <PlayerName>$player</>?//<portrait=normal>Well… You know my uncle pretty well, though, so that counts.

Text.SourceString: Growing up, I used to love joining my dad on his early morning fishing trips.//<portrait=happy>Don't let him hear this, but I get bored of fishing real quick.
Text.LocalizedString: Growing up, I used to love joining my dad on his early morning fishing trips.//<portrait=happy>Don't let him hear this, but I get bored of fishing real quick.

Text.SourceString: This job, being a scientist, is perfect for me.//<portrait=normal>I’m always on a mission to find something new. Keeps me interested, you see.
Text.LocalizedString: This job, being a scientist, is perfect for me.//<portrait=normal>I’m always on a mission to find something new. Keeps me interested, you see.

Text.SourceString: I haven't visited here during the Summers in ages, so I wouldn't blame anyone for not remembering me.//<portrait=happy>I barely remember them.
Text.LocalizedString: I haven't visited here during the Summers in ages, so I wouldn't blame anyone for not remembering me.//<portrait=happy>I barely remember them.

Text.SourceString: In my defense, I was here only a handful of times as a kid.//I mostly remember just being psyched about exploring the sea.
Text.LocalizedString: In my defense, I was here only a handful of times as a kid.//I mostly remember just being psyched about exploring the sea.

Text.SourceString: Gotta say, I just noticed your eyes. They've got this warm...glow to them.//<portrait=blushing>I could look at you all day.
Text.LocalizedString: Gotta say, I just noticed your eyes. They've got this warm...glow to them.//<portrait=blushing>I could look at you all day.

Text.SourceString: Is it cool to say that? I’m not scaring you, am I?
Text.LocalizedString: Is it cool to say that? I’m not scaring you, am I?

Text.SourceString: I had this idea jobs would be lining up for me as soon as I got my doctorate.//<portrait=surprised>But gosh! That wasn’t the case at all. I was so young and naive.
Text.LocalizedString: I had this idea jobs would be lining up for me as soon as I got my doctorate.//<portrait=surprised>But gosh! That wasn’t the case at all. I was so young and naive.

Text.SourceString: I’m glad I got a job here. If I hadn’t, I’d probably be at a corporation somewhere, testing food or makeup or something, trying for years and years to get decent work experience.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m glad I got a job here. If I hadn’t, I’d probably be at a corporation somewhere, testing food or makeup or something, trying for years and years to get decent work experience.

Text.SourceString: Not that there's anything wrong with it.//Just not the kind of thing I had in mind when I started studying biology.
Text.LocalizedString: Not that there's anything wrong with it.//Just not the kind of thing I had in mind when I started studying biology.

Text.SourceString: I wish I had my own place so I could invite you over for a chat. Or a meal.//Whatever you want to do.
Text.LocalizedString: I wish I had my own place so I could invite you over for a chat. Or a meal.//Whatever you want to do.

Text.SourceString: You can come over to my place, of course.//<portrait=happy>I mean, everyone knows we’re close. Just less privacy, I guess.
Text.LocalizedString: You can come over to my place, of course.//<portrait=happy>I mean, everyone knows we’re close. Just less privacy, I guess.

Text.SourceString: Not sure I'll ever visit the cavern. Being in such a confined space, deep underground...gives me the chills.//It's different from the ocean. The ocean isn't so...claustrophobic.
Text.LocalizedString: Not sure I'll ever visit the cavern. Being in such a confined space, deep underground...gives me the chills.//It's different from the ocean. The ocean isn't so...claustrophobic.

Text.SourceString: I think I saw Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> slip a little sawdust into his tea this morning.//That's odd, right? It's not just me?
Text.LocalizedString: I think I saw Uncle <NPCName>Joko</> slip a little sawdust into his tea this morning.//That's odd, right? It's not just me?

Text.SourceString: I’m still looking for a new place to live. Let me know if you hear of anything, okay?
Text.LocalizedString: I’m still looking for a new place to live. Let me know if you hear of anything, okay?

Text.SourceString: I like <NPCName>Rafael</>, but we're both the quiet types.//<portrait=normal>I don’t think we’ve said ten words to each other in, like, a year. He gets me.
Text.LocalizedString: I like <NPCName>Rafael</>, but we're both the quiet types.//<portrait=normal>I don’t think we’ve said ten words to each other in, like, a year. He gets me.

Text.SourceString: I’m not sure if I’d have liked living at the ranch. I don’t really get along with horses.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m not sure if I’d have liked living at the ranch. I don’t really get along with horses.

Text.SourceString: I like them. They just don’t like me, apparently.//<portrait=normal>Remind me to tell you about the time I went pony riding.
Text.LocalizedString: I like them. They just don’t like me, apparently.//<portrait=normal>Remind me to tell you about the time I went pony riding.

Text.SourceString: Will you be at the Harvest Festival? I hope it won’t rain that day.
Text.LocalizedString: Will you be at the Harvest Festival? I hope it won’t rain that day.

Text.SourceString: There’s a hot spring behind our house. Not sure if it’s functioning, though.//You should check it out now the weather is cooling down. It replenishes your energy!
Text.LocalizedString: There’s a hot spring behind our house. Not sure if it’s functioning, though.//You should check it out now the weather is cooling down. It replenishes your energy!

Text.SourceString: I walked <NPCName>Archie</> to school the other day. But then he found a squirrel he liked, so of course he had to stop and chat.//They seemed to hit it off pretty well.
Text.LocalizedString: I walked <NPCName>Archie</> to school the other day. But then he found a squirrel he liked, so of course he had to stop and chat.//They seemed to hit it off pretty well.

Text.SourceString: Long story short, we were late.
Text.LocalizedString: Long story short, we were late.

Text.SourceString: Where can I get some nice ice cream, you think?
Text.LocalizedString: Where can I get some nice ice cream, you think?

Text.SourceString: Whenever I spot Taco taking a swim in that fountain near the tavern, part of me wishes I could join him.//Looks super refreshing!
Text.LocalizedString: Whenever I spot Taco taking a swim in that fountain near the tavern, part of me wishes I could join him.//Looks super refreshing!

Text.SourceString: Always a treat to see you, <PlayerName>$player</>!
Text.LocalizedString: Always a treat to see you, <PlayerName>$player</>!

Text.SourceString: I like being so close to my nephew. It makes me think about starting a family of my own one day.
Text.LocalizedString: I like being so close to my nephew. It makes me think about starting a family of my own one day.

Text.SourceString: Do you ever think about that?
Text.LocalizedString: Do you ever think about that?

Text.SourceString: Family means a lot to me. Kinda feels like everyone on this island is part of my extended family.
Text.LocalizedString: Family means a lot to me. Kinda feels like everyone on this island is part of my extended family.

Text.SourceString: I guess that’s my way of saying you’re important to me too, <PlayerName>$player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: I guess that’s my way of saying you’re important to me too, <PlayerName>$player</>.

Text.SourceString: I love working here. Would even do it for free!
Text.LocalizedString: I love working here. Would even do it for free!

Text.SourceString: But, uh, don’t tell <NPCName>Ling</>that.
Text.LocalizedString: But, uh, don’t tell <NPCName>Ling</>that.

Text.SourceString: I’m glad you stop by the lab so often.//Gives me something to look forward to.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m glad you stop by the lab so often.//Gives me something to look forward to.

Text.SourceString: I love taking strolls on the beach under the moonlight. There's something about how the starlight reflects off the water...it's downright enchanting.
Text.LocalizedString: I love taking strolls on the beach under the moonlight. There's something about how the starlight reflects off the water...it's downright enchanting.

Text.SourceString: Maybe you’d like to join me sometime.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe you’d like to join me sometime.

Text.SourceString: You smell like a fresh piece of coral, ready for a microscope inspection.
Text.LocalizedString: You smell like a fresh piece of coral, ready for a microscope inspection.

Text.SourceString: Sorry. That’s…uh…supposed to be a compliment.
Text.LocalizedString: Sorry. That’s…uh…supposed to be a compliment.

Text.SourceString: Days like this make me wanna go out and stay out.
Text.LocalizedString: Days like this make me wanna go out and stay out.

Text.SourceString: Days like this make me wanna stay in and sleep the whole day.
Text.LocalizedString: Days like this make me wanna stay in and sleep the whole day.

Text.SourceString: I’m glad I finally resolved my living situation, <PlayerName>$player</>.//Tell you the truth, I was having a really hard time finding my own place anyway.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m glad I finally resolved my living situation, <PlayerName>$player</>.//Tell you the truth, I was having a really hard time finding my own place anyway.

Text.SourceString: I’m terrified of hand puppets.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m terrified of hand puppets.

Text.SourceString: I’ve never told anyone that before. I guess I just wanted you to know.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve never told anyone that before. I guess I just wanted you to know.

Text.SourceString: Whoo, that’s a load off my mind!
Text.LocalizedString: Whoo, that’s a load off my mind!
